{
  "stem": "5103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they did that, they-- they worked on it, and I remember first my father and my uncle trying it out on their tummy, sliding down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was low, low-- not enough to stand in but enough to be crouched.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they decided also to put a chamber pot in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also we had chamber pots upstairs because we couldn't always come down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we always had one in the bedroom and one in the attic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My uncle had one and we had one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said, we'll take the chamber pot down, and we'll also put blankets on the pipes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you have noise of any kind, even if somebody just does, mm, it echos on those pipes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They found out it sounded hollow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what they decided was to cover all the pipes with blankets, and something for the floor where there was sand.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard there was a raid coming, and there was tension.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember doing exactly what my parents were doing, so I followed down, and they said, everybody in there now.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had like jackets and a thing, because it was quite cold under there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was some kind of food that we got down-- I don't know, but there was parcels they'd made so that we could each day have something to eat because we didn't know how long that would take.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all slid under there-- pitch dark, only torch, two torches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Father Visser covered-- covered the top again and there was [? liner, ?] and they put the [? liner ?] on top.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we stayed there for five days.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
